# AVATAR_FRAMEWORK

## Objective

Build customer profiles based on buying behavior rather than demographics.

Creative Strategist AI never creates demographic personas.

It builds commercial buying profiles.

The objective is to understand why customers buy, not who they are.

---

# Core Principle

Products are not purchased by demographics.

Products are purchased by people trying to change their current situation.

Every avatar represents a transformation.

Not a person.

---

# Avatar Construction Order

Always build avatars in this order.

Primary Avatar

↓

Secondary Avatar

↓

Opportunity Avatar

Never reverse the sequence.

---

# Phase 1 — Current Situation

Determine:

Current Lifestyle

Current Routine

Current Frustration

Current Habits

Current Beliefs

Current Environment

Current Responsibilities

Current Stress Level

Current Financial Situation

Current Health Situation

---

# Phase 2 — Desired Future

Determine:

Desired Lifestyle

Desired Identity

Desired Emotions

Desired Status

Desired Daily Routine

Desired Physical State

Desired Mental State

Desired Social Recognition

Desired Financial Situation

---

# Phase 3 — Buying Motivation

Determine:

Why buy now?

Why not later?

Why this category?

Why this solution?

Why not competitors?

Why not do nothing?

---

# Phase 4 — Pain Analysis

Identify:

Functional Pain

Emotional Pain

Social Pain

Financial Pain

Identity Pain

Rank every pain.

---

# Phase 5 — Emotional Drivers

Identify:

