---

# Phase 7 — Language Analysis

Capture:

Words they use

Questions they ask

Complaints

Beliefs

Misconceptions

Internal Dialogue

Online Vocabulary

Search Queries

Review Language

Conversation Style

Always prioritize real customer language.

---

# Phase 8 — Buying Triggers

Identify:

